\c 36 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 36\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Waa'ee Jal'ina Namaa Fi Waa'ee Gaarummaa Waaqayyoo (Geggeessituu warra faarfatootaaf; faarfannaa Daawit garbicha Waaqayyoo)
\m \bd 1\bd* Cubbuun keessa garaa nama jal'aa isa gad fagootti in dubbata; kanaafis Waaqayyoon sodaachuun yaada namichaa keessa hin jiru.
\m \bd 2\bd* Namichi yakka isaa argee akka hin jibbinetti, akka yaada isaatiitti of gowwoomsuu isaa ti.
\m \bd 3\bd* Dubbiin afaan namichaa keessaa ba'u haxxummaa fi gowwoomsaa dha, inni ogummaadhaan hojjechuu, waan gaariis gochuu dhiiseera.
\m \bd 4\bd* Yeroo siree isaa irra jiru illee haxxummaa isaatiif mala in qopheessa, karaa gadhee irra bu'eera, hamaa kan ta'e immoo waan tokko hin tuffatu.
\m \bd 5\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, gaarummaan kee hamma bantiiwwan waaqaa, amanamummaan kees hamma duumessootaa in ga'a.
\m \bd 6\bd* qajeelummaan kee akka tulloota kee jabaatee in dhaabata, firdiin ati kennitus, akka lolaa guddaa ittisa hin qabnee ti; nama, horii, bineensas situ gargaaree oolcha, yaa Waaqayyo!
\m \bd 7\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, gaarummaan kee attam guddaa dha, dinqisiisaa dhas, ijoolleen namootaa gaaddisa bobaa kee jalatti kooluu in galu.
\m \bd 8\bd* isaan wanta mana kee keessa guuteen cidha in godhatu, bishaan laga gammachuu keetiis akka dhugan in goota;
\m \bd 9\bd* burqaan jireenya kennu si bira waan jiruuf, ifa keetiin ificha in argina.
\m \bd 10\bd* Gaarummaa kee warra si beekaniif, qajeelummaa kees warra gara-qajeelotaaf ittuma fufi!
\b 
\m \bd 11\bd* Miilli warra of bokoksanii ana irra hin ejjetin, harki warra jal'ootaas oofee biyyaa ana hin baasin.
\m \bd 12\bd* Ilaa! Warri hamaa godhan gad darbatamanii kufan; deebi'aniis ka'uu hin dandeenye.
\b 
